00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:36.656
There are doctors, academics and bloggers

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.856
who have written countless volumes

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:42.040
on the many facets
of this complex subject.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:47.616
There are fatshionistas
who reclaim their bodies and their beauty

00:06:47.640 --> 00:06:50.576
by wearing fatkinis and crop tops,

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:53.520
exposing the flesh
that we're all taught to hide.

00:06:54.200 --> 00:06:55.776
There are fat athletes

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:59.776
who run marathons,
teach yoga or do kickboxing,

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:04.560
